lass=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p class=\"a5\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">{#3}Буйруқ рақами</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p class=\"a5\" style=\" margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">{#4}Буйруқ қабул қилинган жой</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold;\">Ходимнинг иш жойини ўзгартириш тўғрисида</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">1. </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#6} Ходимнинг фамилияси, исми, отасининг исми</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\"> – </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#7}Ходим ишлаётган ташкилот номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#8}Ходимнинг лавозими номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">ининг меҳнат шартномасида шарт қилиб кўрсатилмаган иш жойи </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#9}Ходим бошқа ишга ўтказилаётган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">дан </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#8}Ходимнинг лавозими номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">дан </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#10}Ходим ўтказилаётган янги лавозим номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">га ўзгартирилсин ва шу кундан унинг </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#10}Ходим ўтказилаётган янги лавозим номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">сифатида фаолият юритиши белгилансин.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">2. Қайд этиб ўтилсинки, иш жойи меҳнат шартномасида кўрсатилмаганлиги ҳамда янги иш жойи ходимнинг аввалги меҳнат вазифаси бўйича ва айни ўша меҳнат шароитларида давом эттирилиши сабабли иш жойини ўзгартириш учун унинг алоҳида розилиги талаб этилмайди.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">3. Мазкур буйруқнинг бажарилиши директор ўринбосари томонидан назоратга олинсин.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold;\">Асос:</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> Ўзбекистон Республикаси Меҳнат кодекси 148-моддаси ва ишлаб чиқариш зарурияти.</span></p>\n<table style=\"border: 0px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 203.50138504155px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#11}Буйруқ чиқарган шахснинг лавозими</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 188.21052631579px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">_________________</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 228.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#12}Буйруқ чиқарган шахснинг Ф.И.О.си</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"